WEBVTT

04:44.600 --> 04:46.190 line:80%
Let's not talk about it anymore.

04:46.190 --> 04:47.360 line:80%
Am I wrong?

04:48.400 --> 04:49.800 line:80%
She may take after her mother

04:49.800 --> 04:51.530 line:80%
with all that delicate beauty,

04:51.870 --> 04:53.400 line:80%
but she has such strength.

04:53.870 --> 04:54.920 line:80%
Let alone a girl—
